If the case is confirmed True Positive browse to Incident module.

Use the Execute button to run the playbook. Choose one playbook to run!

 

Run Playbook : < 01 - Phishing Incident Management > Incident > BTN > Phishing Incident Response > to Automate the procedure.



OR

 

Run Playbook : < 01 - Phishing Incident Management > Incident > BTN > Phishing Incident Response via Approval > to get approval from the SoC Analyst.
